node.text: I saw the negative comments about Jayda Cheaves being cast in the film Bid For Love and was greatly disheartened. It sparked this moment on #GetIntoIt  We as a community have to normalize celebrating each other! I have a very small role in the film which stars @dawnhalfkenny @blue_kimble @blameitonkway and I was happy to be there 💛 Congrats to the writers, director & producers 🙌🏽🙌🏽 waiting on the next one 🙏🏽
